{"tid":357881,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"老公不停中出，官恩娜（Ella） 曝已懷第二胎","createTime":"2017-08-13T09:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T12:35:43.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"192e8f873f508993318baa5df2a1138b84872190","tid":357881,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"香港知名歌手官恩娜（Ella）曾罹患俗稱面癱的「貝爾氏麻痺」，姣好的面容一度臉歪嘴斜，所幸就醫後已康復，2015年和中法混血男友Juan結婚後，育有1子B&eacute;B&eacute; G。近來，沉浸在媽媽角色的官恩娜，終於重拾麥克風，返回錄音室籌備新專輯，讓不少歌迷期待偶像的復出。不過，昨Ella分享一家三口短片，驚喜宣布懷第二胎的喜訊！<br />\nElla在IG分享影片，影片中她和兒子在沙灘玩耍，並用樹枝寫下第二個Baby即將在明年1月出生。據悉，Ella肚裡的寶寶已經4個月。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170813/1181394/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170813%2F1181394%2F&d=MR2cyq34YS3YJ7OZFMm7I%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=024accf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170813/1181394/</a><br />\n這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df572e13934417238f07fcaaad8e77748e11a7ec","tid":357881,"uid":8986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:16:23.000Z","msg":"佢個仔唔似混血兒"},{"pid":"3e5798d8413a5f80672188271f8ac2d78e984e93","tid":357881,"uid":28304,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"有時真係好葡萄呢d人<br />\n天生唔使憂柴憂米<br />\n仲可以屌明星<br />\n幸福家庭，人生勝利組<br />\n我就踎係公屋，為兩餐搏殺<br />\n同做奴隸冇咩分別"},{"pid":"c7180cbdb1ce12ffaeaebbf519e362b259768960","tid":357881,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T12:35:43.000Z","msg":"洋腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}